name: Erin Dewey Lennox
bio: ERIN DEWEY LENNOX is a writer / comedian based in Los Angeles, CA. She has performed at clubs, colleges, and alternative venues in over 30 states and at the Women in Comedy Festival, the Cape Fear Comedy Festival, the Out of Bounds Comedy Festival, and at an impromptu roast of her grandfather. She has written for ESPN, MTV, NFL Gameday, and McSweeney's. She also writes a lot of the commercials you fast forward through. Erin studied journalism at the University of North Carolina Chapel Hill and drank a lot at football games.
